<item>
      <title>Partners In Health Celebrates 10 Years in Rwanda</title>
      <link>http://www.pih.org/media/Partners-In-Health-Celebrates-10-Years-in-Rwanda</link>
      <guid>http://www.pih.org/media/Partners-In-Health-Celebrates-10-Years-in-Rwanda</guid>
    
    <description><![CDATA[<div><figure class="bp-header-photo" style="margin-left:0;width:100%;max-width:600px;"><iframe src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/132446931" width="100%" frameborder="0" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe>
<br><small><figcaption><p>
	Listen as Ophelia Dahl, chair of Partners In Health&rsquo;s board and former executive director, tells the story of PIH&rsquo;s involvement in Rwanda and some of its successes over the last decade. PIH and its sister organization, Inshuti Mu Buzima, work in partnership with Rwanda&rsquo;s Ministry of Health.</p>
